<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-GLhlTQ8iRABdZLl6O3oVMWSktQOp6b7In1Zl3/Jr59b6EGGoI1aFkw7cmDA6j6gD" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="icon" type="imagem/png" href="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1007776867283120270/1072205598864703539/b6212d50-fa41-48c5-8388-ba97bf9a70e6-removebg-preview.png" />
    <title>Página Inicial</title>
</head>

<style>
  body{
    background-color: #E9E9E9;
  }

  .card {
    background-color: transparent;
    max-width: 200px;
    display: inline-block;
    margin: auto;
    text-align: center;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    border: none;
    padding: 30px;
    margin: 20px;
}

  .cardAtendimento {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    background-color: #D7D7D7;
    max-width: 270px;
    display: inline-block;
    margin: auto;
    text-align: center;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: 0.9s;
    padding: 30px;
    margin: 20px;
}

  .cardAtendimento:hover{
    transform: scale(1.1);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
  }

  #responsavel{
    min-width: 80px;
    border: solid 1px #7C7A7B;
    background-color: #FADEC9;
    border-radius: 30px;
  }

  #pet{
    min-width: 80px;
    border: solid 1px #7C7A7B;
    background-color: #E8DEEE;
    border-radius: 30px;
  }

  #tipoDeAtendimento{
    display: flex;
    text-align: left;
    margin-left: 15px;
  }

  .nav-item{
    margin-right: 10px;
  }
</style>

<body>

  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg">
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="/api/">PetShop</a>
      <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
        <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
      </button>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
            <ul class="navbar-nav">
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary" aria-current="page" href="/api/" role="button">Home</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary" aria-current="page" href="/api/pet" role="button">Pet</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary" aria-current="page" href="/api/responsavel" role="button">Responsável</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary" aria-current="page" href="/api/atendimento" role="button">Atendimento</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="btn btn-outline-success" aria-current="page" href="/api/sigin" role="button">Entrar</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="btn btn-outline-danger" aria-current="page" href="/api/logout" role="button">Logout</a>
            </li>
  
            </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

    <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide">
        <div class="carousel-indicators">
          <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1" style="background-color: #18191C;"></button>
          <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2" style="background-color: #18191C;"></button>
          <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3" style="background-color: #18191C;"></button>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1007776867283120270/1072213917465575474/Ate_50_OFF_em_racoes_selecionadas.png?width=1440&height=525" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block" style="color: #18191C;">
              <h4>Bem-vindo ao PetShop!</h4>
              <p>Venha com o seu amiguinho para podermos cuidar dele da melhor forma possível.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1007776867283120270/1072212946513563658/4.png?width=1440&height=525" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1007776867283120270/1072212945846673408/5.png?width=1440&height=525" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="prev">
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="next">
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center font-weight-bold mt-5 p-5">
        <h4 class="mb-4">PetShop Marimar</h4>
        <p>Nós acreditamos que todos os animais merecem um tratamento especial e carinho. Por isso, oferecemos um serviço de alta qualidade no nosso petshop. Nossos funcionários são treinados e amam animais, garantindo que seu pet receba o melhor cuidado possível. Além disso, contamos com produtos de alta qualidade para garantir a saúde e bem-estar de seu animal de estimação. Venha nos visitar e experimente a diferença em cuidar de seu pet com amor e carinho!</p>
      </div>

      <hr>

      <div class="row justify-content-center text-center mt-5" aling="center">
        <h4 class="mb-4">Cuidamos de diversos animais</h4>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1007776867283120270/1072207647396335676/054296ca-15be-4b7d-b973-3c1a0120c008-removebg-preview.png" alt="" class="rounded-circle"  width="140" height="140">
          <h5 class="mt-3">Gatos</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1007776867283120270/1072205598864703539/b6212d50-fa41-48c5-8388-ba97bf9a70e6-removebg-preview.png" alt="" class="rounded-circle"  width="140" height="140">
          <h5 class="mt-3">Cachorros</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1007776867283120270/1072207087582576640/download-removebg-preview_1.png" alt="" class="rounded-circle"  width="140" height="140">
          <h5 class="mt-3">Hamster</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1007776867283120270/1072208351590621264/13752897-bonito-desenho-de-chinchila-pulando-vetor-removebg-preview.png" alt="" class="rounded-circle"  width="140" height="140">
          <h5 class="mt-3">Chinchilas</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1007776867283120270/1072208352114917397/0ea1dd77-1cec-4c7d-8167-cc4335998a2f-removebg-preview.png" alt="" class="rounded-circle"  width="140" height="140">
          <h5 class="mt-3">Coelhos</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1007776867283120270/1072207087834247318/3513815-ilustracoes-de-doninha-desenho-furao-vetor-removebg-preview.png" alt="" class="rounded-circle"  width="140" height="140">
          <h5 class="mt-3">Furão</h5>
        </div>
      </div>

        <hr>

       

        <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5 g-3">
          <h4 class="mb-4 text-center">Atendimentos agendados</h4>
          <% for(response of response) {%>
          <div class="cardAtendimento col-md-3">
            <h5 class="mt-3">Atendimento</h5>
            <p id="tipoDeAtendimento" class="col lg-2"><%= response.tipo %></p>
            <div class="container">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm">
                  <p id="responsavel" class="col lg-2"><%= response.responsavel[0].nome %></p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm">
                  <p id="pet" class="col lg-2"><%= response.pet[0].nome %></p>
                </div>
              </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                  <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#<%= response._id %>">
                      Detalhamento
                  </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
           <!-- Modal de cada Card -->
        <div class="modal fade" id="<%= response._id %>" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
            <div class="modal-content">
              <div class="modal-header">
                <h1 class="modal-title fs-5" id="exampleModalLabel">Detalhamento</h1>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
              </div>
              <div class="modal-body">
                <div class="mb-2">
                  <label for="nome" class="form-label"><strong>Tipo:</strong></label>
                  <p><%= response.tipo %></p>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-2">
                  <label for="nome" class="form-label"><strong>Descriçao:</strong></label>
                  <p><%= response.descricao %></p>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-2">
                  <label for="nome" class="form-label"><strong>Data:</strong></label>
                  <p><%= response.data %></p>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-2">
                  <label for="nome" class="form-label"><strong>Hora:</strong></label>
                  <p><%= response.hora %></p>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-2">
                  <label for="nome" class="form-label"><strong>Responsável:</strong></label>
                  <p><%= response.responsavel[0].nome %></p>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-2">
                  <label for="nome" class="form-label"><strong>Pet:</strong></label>
                  <p><%= response.pet[0].nome %></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Fechar</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
          <% } %>
        </div>



        <section class="mt-5">
          <!-- Footer -->
          <footer class="text-center text-black" style="background-color: #E8DEEE;">
            <!-- Grid container -->
            <div class="container p-4 pb-0">
              <!-- Section: CTA -->
              <section class="">
                <p class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                  <span class="me-3">Cadastre-se gratuitamente.</span>
                  <a class="btn btn-outline-light btn-rounded text-black" aria-current="page" href="/api/signup" role="button">Cadastrar</a>
                </p>
              </section>
              <!-- Section: CTA -->
            </div>
            <!-- Grid container -->
        
            <!-- Copyright -->
            <div class="text-center p-3" style="background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);">
              © 2023 Copyright:
              <a class="text-black" href="/api/">PetShop</a>
            </div>
            <!-- Copyright -->
          </footer>
          <!-- Footer -->
        </section>



      <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-w76AqPfDkMBDXo30jS1Sgez6pr3x5MlQ1ZAGC+nuZB+EYdgRZgiwxhTBTkF7CXvN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>